---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="TELOS | Problems Missions Goals and Life Direction" description="Personal framework for tracking purpose and direction in life">
  <main class="relative z-10 pt-28 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-gradient mb-4">TELOS Framework</h1>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-secondary">
          TELOS is my personal framework for tracking purpose and direction in life. It's a structured way to document Problems I want to solve, Missions to address them, Goals to achieve, and Metrics to track progress. The name comes from the Greek word for purpose or end goal.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problems -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent bg-accent/20 px-3 py-1 rounded">P</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-text-primary">Problems</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-6">
          The most important issues I see in the world that need solving.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent shrink-0">P1</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Complexity vs Complicated Thinking</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-text-secondary">
                  Everything is complex in today's hyperconnected world, yet the predominant thinking and tools are ones catering for a complicated world.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent shrink-0">P2</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Poor Mental Models</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-text-secondary">
                  People have poor models for how the world works, and they lack the tools to properly improve them.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Missions -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand bg-brand/20 px-3 py-1 rounded">M</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-text-primary">Missions</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-6">
          My approaches to addressing these problems.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand shrink-0">M1</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Promote Complex Methodologies</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-text-secondary">
                  Increase the understanding and use of complex methodologies to problems.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand shrink-0">M2</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Build Coherent Social Architectures</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-text-secondary">
                  Create social architectures that increase the coherence within the system to be strategic.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <section class="border-t border-border-subtle pt-8">
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-tertiary italic">
          TELOS is a living framework that evolves as I learn and grow. It's not about rigid adherence to a plan, but about having a north star to guide decisions and actions.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
